name: FALLEN ANGEL
description:
Fallen Angel! Why are you scared?
Why you dwelt alone in shadows?
Why you tighten your fists?
Why threaten the whole life?
I know, Afraid to love,
Let tenderness pour from your eyes to irrigate the earth and the light of love, silently, will lift you in heaven again.
                            
           ~ ALEXIS KARPOUZOS ~
